             were indicted for <rs id="t18230219-136-off765" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230219-136-off765" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230219-136-off765" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230219-136-cd766" type="crimeDate">17th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230219-136-off765 t18230219-136-cd766"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230219-136-off768 t18230219-136-cd766"></join>, three counterpanes, value 20 s.; nine sheets, value 15 s.; three night-gowns, value 3 s.; six table-cloths, value 12 s.; ten shifts, value 10 s.; twenty petticoats, value 20 s.; twenty-five napkins, value 20 s.; two pair of stays, value 2 s., and a bag, value 1 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18230219-136-victim1245" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Phillips
                  <interp inst="t18230219-136-victim1245" type="surname" value="Phillips"></interp>
